299635.「ただいまより 第１１回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加す:
It's time to introduce the fierce beauties
who will be participating in this year's
11th Annual Astoltia Queen Contest!

299636.「前大会で 好成績をおさめ\n 見事 出場権を獲得した ３名に加え……:
And now, joining the 3 winners with excellent
results from last year's tournament...

299637.「ファルパパ神による特別推薦枠 ２名と\n 総勢４８人の予選を勝ち抜いた 上位３:
With 2 special recommendations from Falpapa,
as well as 3 winners from 48 preliminary
contestants, 8 beauties will aim for the top!

299638.「まずは 前大会の覇者が 堂々の登場だ！\n からクモ 予選２位通過から まさか:
First, we have the winner from the previous round! The sweet spider who came in second in the qualifiers, unexpectedly winning by
a landslide!

299639.「今回も 巻き起こせ\n かわいクモ ネバっこい 大グモ旋風！\n スパイダーガ:
Let's fill the world with a whirlwind of cute,
little spiders! The spider girl herself,
Webney!

299640.「……正直なところ バルディスタの\n いち兵士にすぎない私が 優勝するなんて\:
The idea that me, a mere soldier of Valdista
could ever hope to win... it really spun my
silk!

299641.「でも たくさんの人に 投票してもらえて\n クイーンになれて……恥ずかしクモあ:
But I'm so happy so many people chose to
vote for me... I'm pretty flustered, but thank
you all so much for sticking with me!

299642.「こうなったら ずうずうしクモ\n 狙ってやりまシュ 前人未到の ２連覇をッ！\:
If you all hang around, I'm gonna be the best
spider I can and go for an unprecedented
second win! Please lend me your support!

299643.「家族の過ち 民の期待 過去 未来……\n すべてを背負って それでも 少女は\:
Her family's mistakes, her people's
expectations, her past and future... Bearing
it all, she still looks ahead with resolve.

299644.「今度こそ 頂点の栄光を その手に！\n 時をかける王女 メレアーデ！:
Grasp the pinnacle of glory in your hand!
The Time Traveling Princess, Mereade!

299645.「前回は みんなのおかげで ２位という\n すばらしい結果を 手にすることができ:
Thanks to you all, I was able to come in
second place last time! I felt so happy... I
couldn't have done it without you!

299646.「でもね 今より もっと上があるのなら……\n そこを目指す 私でいたい。\n:
However... if there's a chance to be better,
then I have to take it. I want to be the
Queen... I want to be number one.

299647.「だから みんな 応援よろしくにゃん♪: That's why, I need your support! Meow!

299648.「……ご ごめんなさい！\n 今の ナシっ！: S...sorry about that! Pay no mind!

299649.「続いては 熱烈なファンを 多数かかえる\n 前回３位の このお方！:
Next up is our third place finisher! She's got
quite a lot of passionate fans!

299650.「さあ 聞かせてくれ その声を！\n いやしてくれ あのワザで！\n アラハギー:
I wanna hear that cute voice! Heal me with
your magic! The Blue Guide of Al-Ahagiro,
Seraphi!

299651.「わーい！ また みんなと会えて\n すっごく うれしい！ もう 待ちきれないか:
Yaaay! I'm so happy to see everyone again!
I just can't wait anymore! A Midheal for you!

299652.「……って あれれ？\n 失敗しちゃった。: ...huh? I think I messed it up...

299653.「えへへ……まだ\n ベホイミに 慣れてないからかなあ？\n いつものやつで も:
Ehehe... I guess I'm not used to using Midheal
yet, huh? I'll go with my usual instead!

299655.「続きましては ファルパパ神による\n 特別推薦枠から ２名をご紹介！\n まず:
Next on our list, I'd like to introduce the
two who were recommended by Falpapa!
First up, we have...

299656.「ここの連中を 全員 ブチのめせば\n アストルティアで イチバン強ぇ オンナに:
If I beat the crap out of all y'all, I'll
be the strongest woman in Astoltia! Come on!
I'll take you all on!

299658.「……改めまして。特別推薦枠 まずはこの方！\n この世のすべてを コブシで 解:
Once again... this is the first of our
recommendations! She'll solve any problem with
a fight! She's reckless, rowdy, and ready!

299659.「あこがれの エックスさぁーん！\n ケイトの勇姿 見てますかぁーっ？\n 野獣:
She aspires to be just like X!! Have
you been watching how brave she is?!
Kate, the biggest fan girl!

299660.「なんだか わかんねェけど 甘ぇモンを\n しこたま作りゃあ テッペン取れるらし:
I'm not really sure what all this's about,
but I heard bein' all sweet is a way to make
it to the top.

299661.「……いいぜ。なんだって やってやらぁ！\n クイーンとやらに なって エックス:
It's fine... I don't care! I'll do whatever it
takes! I'll become the Queen, and dedicate
my victory to the great X!

299662.「さあ 続きまして\n 特別推薦枠 ふたりめは……: And now, our second special recommendation...

299663.「ンフ<heart> くだらぬ催しだな。\n ゆりかごの末裔よ。:
Hmph...<heart> What a foolish event.
Descendants of the Cradle...

299664.「だが 誉めてやろう ひとつだけ。\n 支配者を決めるという 決戦の場に\n こ:
However, credit shall be given where credit
is due. I commend you for inviting me to this
battle in deciding who will be ruler!

299665.「服従せよ ジア・クトに。\n さすれば 愛でてやろう お前も。\n ジア・クト:
You must obey Dia Kut. Pledge your loyalty,
and we shall show you love. Become one
with the Dia Kut telecrystal.

299666.「……以上。ファルパパ神による\n 特別推薦枠 ふたりめは\n 完美なる念晶体:
...and that's all. Falpapa's second
recommendation was Dia Lumina, the
perfect telecrystal...

299667.「さあ 今度こそ 気を取りなおして\n まいりましょう！ ここからは 激しい予選:
Okay, let's get back on track! Next up are the
three winners who made it through the
intense qualifying rounds!

299668.「まずは この方！\n 最強の魔王にして 最恐のクイーンが\n ショコラフォンテ:
First off, here she is! The most powerful
Demon King and most fearsome Queen has
returned to the Chocolat Castle!

299669.「前回に引きつづき 今回も クイーンの栄冠は\n バルディスタが 手にするのか！:
Will Valdista be crowned Queen again, just as
she did once before?! The Ice Witch who
brings forth death, Valeria!

299670.「ふん……しばらく 留守にしている間に 何やら\n 妙な連中が 幅を利かせている:
Hmph... it seems while I was away, a strange
lot has decided to spread their wings. The
people of Astoltia are still sweet, I see.

299671.「もう一度 その身に たたき込んでやろう。\n 誰が 真のクイーンなのかを！:
Let me beat it into your heads once more.
Who is the true Queen?!

299672.「……二度は 言わん。\n 私に ついてこい。: I will not say it again... Come with me.

299673.「続きまして 前回は 推薦枠での参戦だった\n このお方！ 心かき乱す 笑顔の奥:
Up next, this gal was here last time as one
of our recommendations! You have to wonder
what's behind that heart wrenching smile...

299674.「蠱惑の笑みに秘めた愛！\n 始源の歌姫 リナーシェ！:
With love hidden behind her alluring smile!
The First Diva, Linashe!

299675.「元より 争い事は 好みません。\n 愛の量を 競うことに\n 意味があるのだろ:
I've never agreed with solving things in
conflict. Does it really make sense to compete
for this much love?

299676.「けれど これほどの量の 愛をいただいて……\n どうして 心弾まずに いられま:
But with such an abundance of love... how
could I not be excited? How could I not
answer the call?

299677.「あなたの夢は わたくしの夢。\n クイーンになるという わたくしの夢に……\n:
Your dream is my dream. Would you please help
me in fulfilling my dream of becoming Queen?

299678.「さあ 第１１回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテスト\n 大トリを飾るのは:
And now, last but definitely not least, the
final contestant of the 11th Annual Astoltia
Queen Contest!

299679.「予選通過順位は もちろん １位！\n 広く深く愛される その姿は まさに勇者！:
To no surprise, she qualified in first place!
Deeply loved all over the world and a true
Hero! The Battle Princess of Purity, Anlucia!

299680.「たくさんの 応援のおかげで\n また この舞台に立つことが できました。\n:
It's thanks to all of your support that I'm
able to stand here on this stage again. Thank
you from the bottom of my heart!

299681.「みんなの気持ちに 応えたくて\n 私……さらに 修行を重ねたわ。\n 山にこも:
I truly wanted to give back to you all, so I
trained even harder... I honed my blade and
heart deep within the mountains...

299682.「そして ついに 完成したの……\n 過去最高の チョコレートが！\n ぜひ 食:
And now, I've finally done it... I've created
the most amazing chocolate ever! I really
hope that you'll try it! ♪

299683.「……以上 ８名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
And so... these 8 beauties will compete to see
who is most deserving to be called Queen.

299684.「栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 果たして 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will rise to the top this time?! It's up
to you to decide!

299685.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
Well, what do you think? There's an amazing
selection of beautiful women for you to choose
this time. Who's your favorite?

299686.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n あなたの持つ票を 投じてあげ:
If you think any of these beauties deserves
to be Queen, then cast your votes!

299687.「なお 投票につきましては 集計係モカの所で\n おこなっていただくことに なっ: Please go and see Mocha if you'd like to vote.

299688.「票を投じましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
After voting, come back and see me so we
can chat. I'll be waiting outside!

299689.「ただいまより 第１１回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発:
We will now announce the results of the
11th Annual Astoltia Queen Contest!

299690.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who is worthy of being crowned Queen of our
Chocolat Fontenay Castle?! The results are
in!!

299691.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please look to the
stage!
